    <stitle>FRONT STEER AXLE: EATON E1200I I-BEAM - LUBRICATION</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>LUBRICATION</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="lubricate" graphiccount="0">
            <title>KINGPINS, THRUST BEARINGS AND TIE ROD ENDS</title>
            <para>For lubrication intervals and type of lubricant, refer to GROUP 10 - LUBRICATION in the CTS-5000
                Master Service Manual.
            </para>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>If it is difficult to grease either the upper or lower bushing, try greasing the bushings with
                        the vehicle jacked up and supported on axle stands to improve grease flow and help flush out
                        contamination.
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
